Rating: 4
These were great! I used black raspberry preserved instead of strawberry, and added a light glazing. For my glaze I mixed 1/2 cup powdered sugar, 2 tsp milk and 1/8 tsp vanilla extract. Just mix these three ingredients together and drizzle quickly back and forth over all the pastries. Next time I think I will try blackberry preserves or something with maple syrup.

